This project uses a labeled X-ray dataset containing **9000+ images** of knees for osteoarthritis detection and grading.

### üóÇÔ∏è Main Folders

| Folder        | Purpose                          |
|---------------|----------------------------------|
| `train/`      | Training set                     |
| `val/`        | Validation set                   |
| `test/`       | Testing set                      |
| `auto_test/`  | For automated predictions export |

Each of these folders contains 5 subfolders corresponding to OA severity grades:

/0/ ‚Üí Normal (Grade 0)
/1/ ‚Üí Doubtful
/2/ ‚Üí Mild
/3/ ‚Üí Moderate
/4/ ‚Üí Severe (Grade 4)


| Grade | Description                                      |
|-------|--------------------------------------------------|
| 0     | Normal, no signs of osteoarthritis               |
| 1     | Doubtful joint space narrowing                   |
| 2     | Definite osteophytes, possible narrowing         |
| 3     | Moderate osteophytes, clear narrowing            |
| 4     | Severe narrowing, sclerosis, deformity           |
